body:
@Kami Nana the MC hasn't been seen since the graduation part, however the lez friend does mention that she hasn't told him where FMC is in the epilogue so they are keeping in touch at the very least. It's only been around a year after graduation so them still talking is very likely.

I will also say that I'm not excusing that what she did is wrong, but given how things played out its not entirely her fault. She does take blame for her compliance, and the teacher obviously for being the main culprit. But MC did indirectly cause her insecurity that lead to her further falling in to the teacher's traps along with nobody clearing up the confession misunderstanding.

At the end, it's just an unfortunate situation that I hope ends if and when the MCs get together since I believe that she learned and bettered herself after all she's been through. Teenagers do make stupid mistakes, even more if they're emotional and insecure like she was at the start.
